  13:/Users/reza.kalfane/Workspaces/Daisy/DaisyExamples/libDaisy/src/per/sai.h ****  * 
  14:/Users/reza.kalfane/Workspaces/Daisy/DaisyExamples/libDaisy/src/per/sai.h ****  * DMA Transfer commands must use buffers located within non-cached memory or use cache maintenance
  15:/Users/reza.kalfane/Workspaces/Daisy/DaisyExamples/libDaisy/src/per/sai.h ****  * To declare an unitialized global element in the DMA memory section:
